refsection.para:
      The following function computes the RR2 scrambling 
	  for the i-th dimension of a point set with s dimensions, 
	  using the bases in the matrix b.

refsection.programlisting:
      
s=3;
primemat=number_primes100();
b=primemat(1:s);
for i=1:s
    sigma=RR2Scrambling(s,i,b);
    sigmastr=strcat(string(sigma),",");
    mprintf("i=%d, [%s]\n",i,sigmastr);
end
